 by Schrodinger equation:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left(\begin{array}{c}
c_{0}^{\prime}\\
c_{1}^{\prime}
\end{array}\right)=e^{-i\widehat{H}^{\mathrm{el}}dt/\hbar}\left(\begin{array}{c}
c_{0}\\
c_{1}
\end{array}\right),\label{eq:EhrenfestPropagation}
